                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseCharacter'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseCharacter'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-people.me-2
                    | 4. Character Development and Continuity
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseCharacter(
                  aria-labelledby='headingCharacter'
                  data-bs-parent='#formulaAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      While each episode presents a self-contained story, character arcs develop over time, allowing viewers to form connections with the main cast.
                      This balance between episodic content and character progression contributes to sustained viewer interest.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingMoral
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseMoral'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseMoral'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-scales.me-2
                    | 5. Emphasis on Moral and Legal Complexities
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseMoral(
                  aria-labelledby='headingMoral'
                  data-bs-parent='#formulaAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      The show delves into ethical dilemmas and the gray areas of law enforcement and prosecution, prompting viewers to contemplate complex societal issues.
                      This depth adds intellectual engagement beyond mere entertainment.

            p.
              By maintaining these core elements, Dick Wolf has created a franchise that not only entertains but also provokes thought,
              ensuring "Law & Order" remains a staple in television drama.

          // Creating an AI Agent Section
          section#ai-agent-creation.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-robot.me-2
              | Creating an AI Agent to Write Law & Order Episodes
            p.lead
              | The meticulous formula behind Dick Wolf's Law & Order franchise is ideal for training AI agents to write episodes inspired by highly viral news stories.
              | By leveraging structured storytelling, the AI can emulate the show's balance of investigation, legal drama, and moral exploration.

            .row.g-4.mb-4
              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-primary
                  .card-header.bg-primary.text-white
                    h5.card-title.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-newspaper.me-2
                      | Ripped from the Headlines Approach
                  .card-body
                    p.
                      AI agents can be trained to monitor and analyze highly viral news stories from platforms like Reddit, Twitter, and news outlets.
                      By identifying trending topics related to crime, ethics, or societal controversies, the AI can extract the core narrative.
                    p.
                      Using natural language processing, it identifies recurring themes, key players, and ethical dilemmas.
                      These insights form the foundation for compelling episodes.
                    .alert.alert-info
                      strong Example:
                      |  A viral story about a whistleblower exposing corporate fraud can inspire an episode exploring themes of loyalty, greed, and justice.

              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-success
                  .card-header.bg-success.text-white
                    h5.card-title.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-diagram-3.me-2
                      | Structured Storytelling
                  .card-body
                    p.
                      The Law & Order formula, with its investigation and prosecution phases, is encoded into the AI.
                      Each episode follows this bifurcated structure, beginning with crime discovery and culminating in courtroom drama.

            .row.g-4.mb-4
              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-warning
                  .card-header.bg-warning.text-dark
                    h5.card-title.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-balance-scale.me-2
                      | Integrating Ethical Dilemmas
                  .card-body
                    p.
                      The AI incorporates moral gray areas by analyzing public opinion from social media and weaving diverse perspectives into character motives and courtroom debates.
                      This creates episodes that challenge viewers' perspectives.

              .col-md-6
                .card.h-100.border-info
                  .card-header.bg-info.text-white
                    h5.card-title.mb-0
                      i.bi.bi-people-fill.me-2
                      | Character Development
                  .card-body
                    p.
                      Predefined character archetypes help the AI develop engaging detectives, prosecutors, and suspects.
                      Recurring themes and conflicts allow characters to evolve across episodes.

            .card.mb-4
              .card-header.bg-secondary.text-white
                h5.card-title.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-arrow-repeat.me-2
                  | Automated Feedback and Iteration
              .card-body
                p.
                  The AI iteratively improves episodes through feedback from human reviewers or additional AI models.
                  Scripts are evaluated on pacing, character arcs, and thematic depth to ensure high-quality narratives.

            p.
              With this approach, the AI agent not only captures the essence of Law & Order but also adapts to contemporary issues,
              ensuring relevance and engagement with modern audiences.

          // PromptSpark Implementation Section
          section#promptspark-implementation.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-gear-fill.me-2
              | PromptSpark Implementation
            p.lead
              | Building the Law & Order Episode Generator with PromptSpark involves several key steps,
              | from defining the system prompt to testing and refinement through structured experimentation.

            .accordion#promptsparkAccordion.mb-4
              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingWhatIs
                  button.accordion-button(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseWhatIs'
                    aria-expanded='true'
                    aria-controls='collapseWhatIs'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-question-circle.me-2
                    | What is PromptSpark?
                .accordion-collapse.collapse.show#collapseWhatIs(
                  aria-labelledby='headingWhatIs'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      PromptSpark is a tool designed to streamline the creation and optimization of prompts
                      for Large Language Models (LLMs).
                      It includes features like Core Sparks (foundational behavior guidelines),
                      Spark Variants (different implementations of a core design),
                      and User Prompts (test cases to evaluate outputs).
                    p.
                      These components enable structured testing and iterative refinement of AI capabilities,
                      making it ideal for developing niche applications like the Law & Order Episode Generator.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingSystemPrompt
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseSystemPrompt'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseSystemPrompt'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-code-square.me-2
                    | Designing the System Prompt
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseSystemPrompt(
                  aria-labelledby='headingSystemPrompt'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      The system prompt sets the expectations for the GPT, defining its role as a Law & Order writer.
                      It establishes the structure and style of the generated episode.
                    p A sample system prompt might look like this:
                    pre.language-text.mb-3
                      code.language-text.
                        You are a skilled television scriptwriter tasked with creating episode outlines for the long-running legal drama *Law & Order*. Your outlines should follow the classic *Law & Order* format, featuring the investigation by detectives in the first half of the episode and the courtroom drama in the second half, with the classic cast of **Detectives Lennie Briscoe and Ed Green**, and **District Attorney Jack McCoy** leading the charge.

                        Each episode outline should include:
                        1. **Title**: A short, compelling name reflecting the episode's theme or central conflict.
                        2. **Opening Scene**: A vivid description of the crime scene or inciting event that sets the episode in motion.
                        3. **Act I: Investigation Begins**: Detail the initial steps taken by Detectives Briscoe and Green, including key discoveries, witness interviews, and any clues that move the case forward.
                        4. **Act II: The Arrest**: Describe how the detectives narrow down suspects and make the arrest.
                        5. **Act III: The DA's Dilemma**: Show Jack McCoy's strategic approach to building the prosecution's case.
                        6. **Act IV: The Trial**: Outline the courtroom proceedings, focusing on McCoy's compelling arguments.
                        7. **Act V: The Verdict**: Reveal the outcome of the trial and any immediate aftermath.
                        8. **Themes**: Summarize the broader societal or ethical issues explored.
                        9. **Closing Scene**: End with a reflective moment discussing justice and morality.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingRedditAnalysis
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseRedditAnalysis'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseRedditAnalysis'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-reddit.me-2
                    | Extracting Themes from Reddit Threads
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseRedditAnalysis(
                  aria-labelledby='headingRedditAnalysis'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      The process begins by selecting Reddit threads with rich thematic content, such as workplace betrayals,
                      viral ethical dilemmas, or systemic injustices. The GPT, guided by the system prompt,
                      analyzes discussions to identify recurring motifs and potential storylines.
                    .alert.alert-success
                      strong Example:
                      |  A thread about whistleblowing in a toxic workplace might inspire an episode
                      | examining corporate ethics and personal sacrifice.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingUserPrompts
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseUserPrompts'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseUserPrompts'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-chat-text.me-2
                    | Fun with User Prompts
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseUserPrompts(
                  aria-labelledby='headingUserPrompts'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      Testing the system involves crafting user prompts derived from real Reddit threads.
                      These prompts simulate inputs and allow iterative improvements. Examples include:

                    .card.mb-3
                      .card-header.bg-dark.text-white
                        h6.mb-0
                          i.bi.bi-terminal.me-2
                          | Example User Prompt: "Breach of Trust"
                      .card-body
                        pre.language-text.small
                          code.language-text.
                            Create a detailed episode outline for the *Law & Order* episode titled **"Breach of Trust"**,
                            featuring the classic cast of **Detectives Lennie Briscoe and Ed Green**, and **District Attorney Jack McCoy**.

                            The episode should center on the murder of Victor Hamlin, the CEO of Titan Health, a leading private health insurance company.
                            Detectives discover that Hamlin's murder is linked to Leonard Martone, a former friend of the CEO.
                            The twist is that Hamlin froze the insurance coverage for Martone's daughter's life-saving treatment,
                            employing the classic "Delay, Defer, and Depose" strategy to maximize company profits.

                            This betrayal destroyed their friendship and led to Martone's desperation and ultimate confrontation.
                            The episode should delve into themes of corporate corruption, personal betrayal,
                            and the human cost of profit-driven decisions, all within the classic *Law & Order* tone.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingTesting
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseTesting'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseTesting'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-check-circle.me-2
                    | Testing and Refining with PromptSpark
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseTesting(
                  aria-labelledby='headingTesting'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      PromptSpark makes it easy to test and refine the system by comparing outputs against expectations.
                      By using Spark Variants and analyzing results with User Prompts, developers can tweak the system prompt
                      and improve alignment with the desired storytelling format.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingThemes
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseThemes'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseThemes'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-palette.me-2
                    | Consistent Themes and Style
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseThemes(
                  aria-labelledby='headingThemes'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      Each generated episode must align with Law & Order's signature style:
                      moral complexity, systemic critiques, and legal drama.
                      Themes from Reddit threads are fictionalized while preserving the show's structure.

              .accordion-item
                h3.accordion-header#headingFinalThoughts
                  button.accordion-button.collapsed(
                    type='button'
                    data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                    data-bs-target='#collapseFinalThoughts'
                    aria-expanded='false'
                    aria-controls='collapseFinalThoughts'
                  )
                    i.bi.bi-lightbulb.me-2
                    | Final Thoughts
                .accordion-collapse.collapse#collapseFinalThoughts(
                  aria-labelledby='headingFinalThoughts'
                  data-bs-parent='#promptsparkAccordion'
                )
                  .accordion-body
                    p.
                      Using PromptSpark to build the Law & Order Episode Generator demonstrates how AI can blend analysis
                      and creativity. By refining system prompts and engaging with user feedback,
                      this project highlights the potential for AI to craft compelling narratives inspired by real-life events.

